<div class="mt-16 space-y-12">
  <!-- How to Use Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How to Use the Yoga Session Timer</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
      <p class="lead">The Yoga Session Timer above helps you create structured practice sessions with customizable pose durations and sequences. Follow these steps to get started:</p>
      
      <ol class="space-y-3">
        <li><strong>Add Poses:</strong> Select poses from the preset library and set their durations</li>
        <li><strong>Arrange Your Sequence:</strong> Build your practice flow in the order you prefer</li>
        <li><strong>Adjust Settings:</strong> Configure voice guidance and sound preferences</li>
        <li><strong>Start Your Practice:</strong> Use the timer controls to guide your session</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Timer Features</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Pose Management</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>• Select from preset yoga poses</li>
          <li>• Customize duration for each pose</li>
          <li>• Rearrange sequence order</li>
          <li>• Add transition times</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Timer Controls</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>• Start, pause, and reset functions</li>
          <li>• Voice guidance option</li>
          <li>• Sound notifications</li>
          <li>• Visual countdown display</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Can I save my sequences?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Currently, sequences are session-based. We recommend taking a screenshot of your sequence for future reference. Saved sequences feature is coming soon!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do I modify pose duration during practice?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You can pause the timer, adjust the duration in the sequence list, and resume your practice. The timer will continue with the updated duration.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Does the timer work offline?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes! Once the page is loaded, the Yoga Session Timer functions completely offline, allowing you to practice anywhere.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Can I customize the voice guidance?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You can toggle voice guidance on/off using the timer controls. The voice announces pose changes and provides transition alerts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>